headline: Santander (SAN) and Webster Deal Faces Execution Risk, Says Morgan Stanley
summary: Banco Santander, S.A. (NYSE:SAN) ranks among the best undervalued European stocks to buy now. On February 4, Morgan Stanley reduced Banco Santander, S.A. (NYSE:SAN) to Equalweight from Overweight, noting limited upside after a robust stock surge and increased execution risk related to the bank’s growth in the United States amid its announced acquisition of Webster […]
